## Soft-delete fields (entity)

Reusable pattern on Prisma entities:

- `isDeleted` Â· `deletedAt` Â· `deletedBy` Â· `deletionReason` (optional)

Operational queries **must** exclude `isDeleted: true` unless Recovery explicitly requests deleted rows.

## Role matrix

| Role | Soft Delete | Restore | Permanent Delete |
|------|-------------|---------|------------------|
| Normal / Analyst / Viewer | If business rules allow (matrix: Manager+) | No | No |
| Manager | Yes | Yes (scope later) | No |
| Admin | Yes | Yes | No |
| SUPER_ADMIN | Yes | Yes | Yes (type `DELETE`) |

